data.description: Practically new home without the wait for a new build centrally located in the Treasure Valley! Hardwood flooring & 9 foot ceilings create a beautiful great room space perfect for entertaining. Functional kitchen layout w/ central island, granite counters, large corner pantry & gas stove. Ideal split bedroom floor plan. The backyard is your very own Organic fruit orchard including a peach tree, raspberries, blackberries & gooseberries! Backyard includes a patio, shed, and green house!
